<h3 id="with-footnotes-too">With footnotes too!</h3>

<p>Back up your stuff with solid, clean citations. Footnotes can be written in markdown and appear like this.<sup id="fnref:1" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote" rel="footnote">1</a></sup> Use as many as you like.<sup id="fnref:2" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:2" class="footnote" rel="footnote">2</a></sup></p>

